summary: An email from an FBI agent forwarding information about Ghislaine Maxwell's FBAR (Foreign Bank Account Report) filing, identifying Laura Barooshin of the accounting firm Dicicco, Gutman & Co. LLP as the preparer. The email includes an attachment of the FBAR transcript.

keyFacts: Ghislaine Maxwell's FBAR (Foreign Bank Account Report) filing was prepared by Laura Barooshin of the accounting firm Dicicco, Gutman & Co. LLP.
The accounting firm's address is in Woburn, Massachusetts.
The information was communicated via email by an FBI agent from the New York Field Office on July 8, 2020.
The document is part of investigative records, indicating scrutiny of Maxwell's financial disclosures.
The email includes an attachment named 'FBAR 31000155991288 transcript.pdf'.
